---
title: Cheesy Chorizo Crusted Cod with Roast Potatoes, Asparagus and Aioli
description: We love good Chorizo Crusted Cod with Roast Potatoes and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-chorizo-crusted-cod-d30f98d5-10ea4a40.jpg
